  • public class AsyncDeezerTask
extends android.os.AsyncTask<DeezerRequest,java.lang.Void,java.lang.String>
    Wraps a DeezerRequest execution in a background thread. The result (either success or failure) of the request execution will be processed on the UI Thread.
